{"tid":1896582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尚德手足：希望香港人會繼續出嚟，直至公義得到彰顯","createTime":"2020-02-25T08:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T16:03:29.000Z","uid":210495,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e7eecafcac7a380f47c6fb45dd308614a34674af","tid":1896582,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:20:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103142554391351/posts/203261664379439/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103142554391351%2Fposts%2F203261664379439%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=45ff5d20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103142554391351/posts/203261664379439/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n今早以議員身份探訪上年10月被捕的尚德手足，他現時被控一系列縱火罪名，暫未有下一次上庭日子。他的臉孔非常年輕，追問之下，他苦笑應道自己今年23歲，我心一揪，為何弱小的人類只能哭泣？<br />\n<br />\n尚德手足沒有像我傷春悲秋，雖也談不上積極樂觀，但大體仍是向前看，與裡面其他手足生活安好，家人亦體諒支持，還跟我調侃昨日林奠的絕密報告，這群栽害香港前途的庸官必會落地獄！<br />\n<br />\n最後尚德手足想同各位講：「希望疫情過後，香港人會繼續出嚟遊行！場運動可以繼續落去，直至公義得到彰顯！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GxjY0Bh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxjY0Bh.jpg&h=cb32337f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd444f03885560ea23a7b7446b3aa15474b8d57d","tid":1896582,"uid":32836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:22:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0af49b0ca753edf3600313c07a6752334e55e2ac","tid":1896582,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:25:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"814f5d4f4f581e43493223a7ae2dc07a00ffc442","tid":1896582,"uid":188035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7eecafcac7a380f47c6fb45dd308614a34674af","tid":1896582,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:20:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103142554391351/posts/203261664379439/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103142554391351%2Fposts